body:
Hey Guys would mind listening to some songs where I added a simple Pitch Up Effect? Feed back on the song is much appreciated and a rating out of 10. :)

P.S. I'v got permission to do this. Also I've given and provided them Credit. Along with that referencing where I got it from. I'll also add some other songs that will have the same effect. :3

Spektrem - Shine (Original Mix) [Pitch Up Effect] -
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k3_rC6HEC5Y

Capital Cities - One Minute More (WAY Remix) [Pitch Up Effect] -
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xl5XGDDKoy4

Bastille - Pompeii (Audien Remix) [Pitch Up Effect] -
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pMTAaeEuTGQ

Porter Robinson - Sad Machine [Pitch Up Effect] -
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RC9v7RicdOU

Krewella - Live for the Night (Aero Chord Remix) (Pitch Up Effect) -
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a53vJeSc_eE

Rhythmics - Candy (Pitch Up Effect) -
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aO6ao6QaHWs
